main event: A youth reported observing a bright object moving swiftly up and down and sideways in Yonkers, New York.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 2 minutes., The object was described as having a solid color and showed no trail., It was estimated to be moving at speeds of 150 mph., Observers included at least one confirmed witness, a youth., The conclusion stated that the object is not an aircraft.
witness description: a youth who made the report
